  "detailed_description": "<strong>SPACE WARDEN</strong> is Top-Down space action shooter where you as a Space Warden are fighting in the war. The Game will offer various of different missions where you escorting ships, destroying space caravans, destroying enemy bases or trying to defend your own base <br>before enemy attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/1dd9c64c7c55c92b99b06c5dd83b26ed.webp?t=1678971758\" width=300 height=50 /></span><br><br>We leave Earth long time ago (app. at year '2580'), <br>after years searching for a new home we found the solar system which consisted of 12 planets and 2 of which were habitable, since we had no other option we land on one of them. After several  generation on this planet, almost half of the population had moved to a second planet only a few light years away from us. We came across a new planet that contained a new raw material, discovery of this started a war.<br>This material is the reason why this war started and has been going on, for generations...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/089e266a73596b47f583f37bfb9d80b2.webp?t=1678971758\" width=300 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single-player Campaign With 10 Missions.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >+ BONUS MiSSION</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Destructive Environment </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/42cca001bea5a7ecc96c4786a51f8ca8.poster.avif?t=1678971758\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/42cca001bea5a7ecc96c4786a51f8ca8.webm?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/42cca001bea5a7ecc96c4786a51f8ca8.mp4?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use a Lot of different Weapons  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/af5232564fa3fd7edb90437761dce22e.poster.avif?t=1678971758\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/af5232564fa3fd7edb90437761dce22e.webm?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/af5232564fa3fd7edb90437761dce22e.mp4?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Ultra RAY,<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/201fe33eafcf7df78d8c0aa4086ffa08.poster.avif?t=1678971758\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/201fe33eafcf7df78d8c0aa4086ffa08.webm?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/201fe33eafcf7df78d8c0aa4086ffa08.mp4?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>tools including Digger, <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/618fd4848c87e2722f647feb054ea025.poster.avif?t=1678971758\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/618fd4848c87e2722f647feb054ea025.webm?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/618fd4848c87e2722f647feb054ea025.mp4?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>or Automated Turrets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/5c3bf4b3517b19650057418886784a3e.poster.avif?t=1678971758\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/5c3bf4b3517b19650057418886784a3e.webm?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/5c3bf4b3517b19650057418886784a3e.mp4?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/3ee8d692743b4bd6fc42c41657327549.poster.avif?t=1678971758\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/3ee8d692743b4bd6fc42c41657327549.webm?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878180/extras/3ee8d692743b4bd6fc42c41657327549.mp4?t=1678971758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game length is around 90-120 minutes.",
